## Usage

Append entities as JSONL:
```jsonl
{"op":"create","entity":{"id":"p_001","type":"Person","properties":{"name":"Alice"}}}
{"op":"create","entity":{"id":"proj_001","type":"Project","properties":{"name":"Website Redesign","status":"active"}}}
{"op":"relate","from":"proj_001","rel":"has_owner","to":"p_001"}
```

## Query Examples

```bash
# List all entities of a type
python3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/ontology/scripts/ontology.py list --type Person

# Create entity
python3 .../ontology.py create --type Person --props '{"name":"Alice"}'

# Query with filter
python3 .../ontology.py query --type Task --where '{"status":"open"}'

# Get related entities
python3 .../ontology.py related --id proj_001 --rel has_task
```

